    About This Item

    • Classic hotdog design that’s great for tailgates and backyard barbecues.
    • Soft, fabric cover that your dog will love to cuddle up with and hold onto.
    • Plush stuffing inside that makes this toy great for catching, fetching and napping.
    • Squeaker-stuffed for lots of fun during playtime, whether they’re playing solo or you join in for interactive fun.
    • Brings out your furry friend’s inner foodie.

    Hot dog! Finally, a cookout classic you and your dog can share! Getting your dog one of these Frisco Plush Hotdog Dog Toys is a great way to get them involved in your next tailgate or backyard barbecue and oh so cute to boot. The soft cover and plush stuffing make this toy ideal for catching, fetching and napping, and the squeaker-stuffed design keeps your dog interested in their solo games and your interactive play sessions.

    Precautions

    This toy is not recommended for heavy chewers. No toy is indestructible. Supervise your pet when using since small parts can present a choking hazard or internal blockage. Discontinue use if the toy is damaged. Keep out of reach of children.

    Spot clean only.

    Is this toy chew-proof or indestructible?

    This toy is not recommended for heavy chewers. No toy is indestructible. Supervise your pet when using, since small parts can present a choking hazard or internal blockage. Discontinue use if the toy is damaged.

    Where is this toy made?

    This toy is made in China and designed and tested to meet our high-quality standards.

    Is this toy machine washable?

    For best results, spot clean only.
